---
title: Easy Bacon & Veggie Gnocchi Bake with Cheddar Cheese & Parsley
description: Gnocchi has to be the cutest pasta around. These little balls sitting in a herby tomato sauce with pops of bacon, celery and carrot are too irresistible to leave alone. We’re gobbling them up this instant!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-veggie-gnocchi-bake-d4243f82.jpg
